cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

This paper deals with generative modeling of high-dimensional data, specifically images, using a hybrid approach combining latent variable models and autoregressive models. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the focus is on image generation, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category, followed by cs.LG and cs.AI.
